<th><a href="/wiki/Lateral_approximant" title="Lateral approximant" class="mw-redirect">Laterals</a></th>
<td colspan="2">&#160;</td>
<td colspan="2">&#160;</td>
<td>&#160;</td>
<td><i>l</i> <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/l/</span></td>
